{"tid":2447393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對港共宣布疫苗計劃擴大至30-59歲人士的觀點","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T08:02:02.000Z","uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d754ac476d7dd67fd6ee60c0a9b7bdde4484b8","tid":2447393,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:22:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔係50歲-60歲<br />\n<strong>正路應該係&gt;50,跟手就&gt;40</strong><br />\n<br />\n1 )港共預計到只限50-60歲時預約唔會滿,就會好醜怪交唔到功課比共產黨,而如果計埋30歲, 就會出現一針難求的盛況<br />\n<br />\n2) <span class=\"red\">對沖死亡率</span><br />\n已知打完科興見毛澤東的藍絲小同志都係本身有三高,可以估計科興對心臟刺激作用,如果心血管有問題就會歸天<br />\n<br />\n30歲係相對健康比較難死, 有望壓死亡率"},{"pid":"a768ee278213fbdff1abf244a0de5366f7df2970","tid":2447393,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"下一步就係強制封區時強制即場排隊打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n史稱即場派人情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73db6987bee9062cf781356d4bb9468ecc2442d","tid":2447393,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"未夠30<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdfcbb5d625a598dddc99c18412c1dfa2fa021e","tid":2447393,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbd9635.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsbd9635.gif&h=03c2bd84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32ff74c9e879392dcc8d29c996f0fcba57b84dfd","tid":2447393,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"打呢支野其實好笨柒<br />\n<br />\n先唔講呢支針死傷率<br />\n呢支針的有效期只係半年至一年<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">到開放疫苗護照你支針已過左效力<span class=\"red\">要重打</span></span><br />\n比你過到兩關唔等於成功連續過4關"},{"pid":"0853960770b1da344322109c48ef1451cba3fa10","tid":244